    /**
     * @description Matches the singleton document for RKSV fiscal certificate and configuration for a tenant.
     * @path /tenants/{tenantId}/rksvConfig
     * @allow (read) If the user is part of the tenant.
     * @allow (create, update) If the user is an admin of the tenant.
