    /**
     * @description Matches the sub-collection for the RKSV cryptographic signature chain.
     * @path /tenants/{tenantId}/signatures/{signatureId}
     * @allow (read, list) If the user is part of the tenant.
     * @allow (create, update, delete) If the user is an admin of the tenant.
